\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Could I have your name please?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Betty. My real name is Diane but nobody knows me a
s Diane, Betty. When I went to college mother didn't like that name so she said - now I'm going to christe you and all, and I was christened in - in the dorm you know, in - in - with the water, Betty, and nobody ever knew anything but that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 And your address?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Malefant Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 And you're a widow?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 The year you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Oh now - 1940 - 1943 isn't it. How many years is that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 And the year you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 1898, I know that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Where were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 16, Brynbedw Road, Tylorstown. Brynbedw Terrace it was in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 How many years did you live in the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 All - all - until I was married you see. We - we were all born - in the house and we all of them that died died in that
 house, my mother, my father, my sister, my brother was killed and his body was brought back there. And then the rest of us are all alive you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 There was six girls and three boys. And the baby died you see in infancy, you see, the little baby who died couple of months old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Could I have their names and the year they were born? Your oldest brother was Meredith?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 That's right, 1896 he was born. You've got that down haven't you? Yes, what do you want now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Betty, that's you, 1898?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Yes. Gwladys Averina, that's 1899. 1901, 190 -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Ealeanor Maud. Glyndwr, 1903?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Yes. Ceinwen 1905.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Mary Tydfil?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Tydfil 1907. Mair Eluned 1909.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Rhiannon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 1912.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 And Deiniol?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 1915.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Would you know how old your father was when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 My father was married at the age of twenty-five. My mother was six months older than him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 And they were married in 1895, so he'd have been about twenty-eight when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Yes, I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Where did he come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 
Oh dear, he was born in Llanddeiniol, Cardiganshire. And he came down South - he went to - you see, what happened to my father - he went to - let me see the beginning now, what happened
. He - there was nothing in the country you see to do, nothing - no work you see in the country. But he - came to the South you see and he went to work - in the pit - and he had an accident. And he broke - that hand, a terrible accident, he broke his righ
t
 hand. And he had a - yu know, slight - little deformity there, with the breaking of it, and scars across there you know. And a funny thing is this, that after that he goes back to Aberystwyth and goes to school. To Aberystwyth Grammar school. And there h
e met his old pal David Owen, Newport, Minister of - of Newport, you know, Mansell - the Mansell Estate there. He died last year. David Owen died only last year. He'd lived all those years, I remember I know where \{ILLEGIBLE\}
 was preaching anywhere he used to land in our house, oh he was a nice man. Only die last year. And his widow is still alive. And out - my - we nearly - they bought }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2370473\charrsid12417786 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786  what}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2370473\charrsid12417786 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2370473\charrsid12417786  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2370473\charrsid12417786 \rquote  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 
name, they nearly bought this house only they didn't want -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Where did he come to originally, did he come to Tylorstown?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 
He came to Tylorstown originally. And we were all - we'd a very nice woman, Mrs David and she was a widow, and she had three men staying with her there. That was what - how she earned her living. Then after the accident he went back to Aberystwyth.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 What age would he be then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 
Well I wouldn't say that he'd be more than - you see, he was married at what did I say well he must have been only about nineteen I think, something like that, I don't really know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 He went back to school then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 He went back to school to Aberytwyth Grammar school, I've got some books here with his name on it if I could put my hand on them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 What did he do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 He did his - training. He did shorthand. And no talk about typing in those da
ys you see. Shorthand and - then - when he - he had got his training he comes back you see. He comes back South, to - and he got a job as a clerk in a colliery office. And there he used to pay hundreds of pounds out every week, you know, pay. And do you k
n
ow, we lived to see him - he became - he had a promotion then from being just a clerk of - of wages and things like that and doing accounts of the men there, he became the compensation clerk so he dealt with all the compensation and do you know then he wa
s
 called - he used to be called John Davis the office, well after that they called him John Davis, Compo. They did. And lot's of people have notice - notice his hand. But do you know he always - he wrote with his right hand you know, he never - he started 
w
riting with his left hand but he went back to his right because he was conscious he didn't want to, but he could use both then. He could do right and left. And he was - very - he was tall smart man. No, no, my mother was short. She was nearly down under h
is - arms you know sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 You don't remember your father ever being out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 No, never. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 You thought your mother was a bit older than your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 She was six months older than him. Yes, she was six months older.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Where did she come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 
My mother was born in Llechwedd. Wait a minute, the name of the house was Llechwedd Llan - Llanafan. Oh there was another name beside Llanafan. That's right. My mother was born in - 11}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \super\insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 
th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 , 9}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \super\insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 , 1870, in Llechwedd, that's the na
me of the house. Llanafan, Llanfigangell. And that's Cardiganshire. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Did she have any jobs before she married?
