\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 No. It was in chapel - you see every night of the week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 During the summer as well?
