\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 The chapel did run a temperance club because the Raccobites is isn't it?
