e went reading in turn, but I don't remember what - what it was, but I do remember reading Bible - so it wasn't Rhodd Mam, it was something after that, some Bible readings they were. And I'll tell you what else we - we did too, we belonged to the W.E.A. A
nd we used to go periodically to a W.E.A. lecture, and we had the most marvellous lecturers.
