\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 'Cos all Cardiganshire people were Liberals weren't they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 What about your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2432619 DT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 She was a Liberal. But she wasn't interested in politics at all. She'd no time to be I don't think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13510004 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786 Why do you think she was a Liberal?
