day Sunday and the school. Cwddr Gweddi. Nos Fawrth. Oh what do you call it, Bible classes. Nos Fawrth - no, Cwrdd Bobl ieuanc, Bible classes on Wednesday. Beit Nos Fawrth. Raccobites on - why I am a Raccobite on Friday, and Saturday we could play. That w
as the only day we had off.
