 father was coming home from work one day and he always called in this - big grocers shop on the way for a chat, and Davy Charles, that was the saon came and said, sgwl John, he said, ma ci bach arna fie, he said, mae c}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
