\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6695053\charrsid12417786 o sisters, the two Miss Armstrong.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7092875\charrsid12417786  Maggie - Armstrong and - what was the other one now -
